text: El Cortez or El Cortez Hotel may refer to: ;Places * El Cortez (Las Vegas), also known as El Cortez Hotel and Casino, in Las Vegas, Nevada, opened in 1941 and listed on the National Register of Historic Places (NRHP) * El Cortez (Reno), also known as El Cortez Hotel, in Reno, Nevada, opened in 1931, NRHP- listed * El Cortez (San Diego), also known as El Cortez Hotel, a former hotel in San Diego, California, NRHP-listed ;Other *El Cortez (film), a film released in 2006, starring Lou Diamond Phillips
